About Us

OUR STORY
GET HOOKED
I practically grew up in a restaurant watching my parents and grandparents as they started opening restaurants in Naples, Florida in 1984. My dad and grandfather spent their time in the kitchen cooking EVERYTHING from scratch, while my mom and grandmother worked in front of the house treating customers as if they were guests in our home. The joy and passion they brought to the restaurant business truly made a great impression on me.
I missed the eating experience I remember as a child, in which our home was practically a restaurant in itself, where family and friends came to feast together -- simply and comfortably.
That’s what Mr. Big Fish is all about. A restaurant where people can relax and feel at home.
Where food is familiar, consistent, and comforting.
Where our guests receive the freshest food with the freshest ingredients, all at a great value. Where patrons recognize the passion that goes into everything we do. Simple. Traditional. Fresh.
We offer crisp salads, hot bread, delicious chowders, fresh local seafood (delivered daily), hand-cut steaks, good wines, and cold beer served in a comfortable atmosphere.
Please do not hesitate to let us know what we can do to make your dining experience better.
